author: paulsalley
title: Stroke of luck
review: I managed to find this set, in great condition with box and instructions on Ebay, for Â£4.  Its the oldest set I own, being only one year younger than me, and although its the most basic set I have, its my favourite.  A small piece of Lego nostalgia, and a fantastic little kit.

author: eman68
title: High playability
review: I remember playing with this plane a lot. It was easy and fast to build and gave me hours of fun time. I will build this again in near future ....
